h predictor (reconstruct at EX)\n","metadata":{"output":"baseline-bench-2d376e0              micro_opt    improvement        ? | Baseline retest for cores/bench\nhyp-20260502-001-r1s0               micro_opt    regression         ? | Iterative shift-subtract divider to shorten EX-stage critical path\nhyp-20260502-002-r1s1               structural   regression         ? | Split M-extension into multi-cycle unit off EX critical path\nhyp-20260502-003-r1s2               predictor    broken             ? | BTB with 1-bit hysteresis for taken branches and unconditional jumps\nhyp-20260502-001-r2s0               micro_opt    broken             ? | Pre-register rd_wdata at MEM/WB boundary to shorten forward + regfile read paths\nhyp-20260502-002-r2s1               structural   broken             ? | Zero-bubble JAL via IF-stage early redirect\nhyp-20260502-003-r2s2               predictor    improvement        ? | Stateless IF-stage static JAL-taken prediction (zero bubble on unconditional jum\nhyp-20260502-001-r3s0               micro_opt    improvement        ? | Fold MUL variants into single 33x33 signed multiplier with sign-ext mux\nhyp-20260502-002-r3s1               structural   broken             ? | Stateless IF-stage backward-taken branch prediction (BTFNT)\nhyp-20260502-003-r3s2               predictor    broken             ? | Stateless IF-stage BTFN conditional-branch predictor (reconstruct at EX)\n","exit":0,"description":"Summarize experiments log","truncated":false},"title":"Summarize experiments log","time":{"start":1777769679828,"end":1777769679830}},"metadata":{"openrouter":{"reasoning_details":[]}},"id":"prt_deb548896001Ipdjin5NCprpAc","sessionID":"ses_214ac9e5cffeU2A2fUH6dUGm1x","messageID":"msg_deb5480c2001KNTlpVLETRPnRQ"}}
