{"type":"text","timestamp":1777780312894,"sessionID":"ses_2140cfe47ffeXzMnBiCl655KRX","part":{"id":"prt_debf6c347001dD0UfkZ4Lg6xVi","messageID":"msg_debf30203001PACuCGt2ZdTknW","sessionID":"ses_2140cfe47ffeXzMnBiCl655KRX","type":"text","text":"Looking at this problem, I need to find a micro_opt that:\n1. Avoids the failure patterns in LESSONS.md (no module splitting, no boolean CSE, no MEM→EX forwarding, no widening IF next_pc mux, no EX-stage pipelined-operand algebraic rewrites)\n2. Matches a winning pattern: arithmetic carry/compare chain shortening via **module-local invariants** (r8s0 pattern, +5.99%)\n\nLet me grep for any prior attempts at pc-register narrowing and review key files.","time":{"start":1777780310856,"end":1777780312892}}}
